==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Provence rose
<hw>Prov"ence rose`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[<ets>Provence</ets> the
place + <ets>rose</ets>.]</ety> <sd>(a)</sd> <def>The cabbage rose
(<spn>Rosa centifolia</spn>).</def> <sd>(b)</sd> <def>A name of many
kinds of roses which are hybrids of <spn>Rosa centifolia</spn> and
<spn>Rosa Gallica</spn>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Provencial</ent>⟦br⟧
